Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.01,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决 断 之 时
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西也很厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧大人 有客人找您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦 让他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧「大人」？ 真臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然随便打开我的货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候变成得这么了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我让他们这么干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「将这个地球打造成我等的理想乡」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第二个阿瓦隆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「别犹豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾丝在加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾米在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘舰团的人到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都像幽灵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神都像被附身了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的居民肯定也会被变成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如此 我当初离开加尔刚蒂亚又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘愿这样下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在打算谋反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是来接我的冲浪龙虾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海贼拉凯奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就跟那个龙虾合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙想指望破废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过雷德那家伙不会帮忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就得这样过一辈子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把帆布展开来收集雨水」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你湿透了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「会感冒的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前观测到的称为「雨」的气象现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未感知到特殊异常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神赐予了我们巨大的恩典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将前往神的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上至高的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为生者而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们要做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为救赎人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而永垂不朽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是为了看这些…而来到这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个疯狂的舰团接下来将驶向加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙我果然受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了从希迪亚斯手中保护大家才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护艾米 为了保护贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护那些人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库盖尔中校发令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雷德少尉进入临战态势」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「听从我的指挥」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请贵官进行判断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判断 你执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我或许从未真正做出过选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解贵官的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校的指令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 你和Striker的战力差有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据不足 无法计算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解贵官的提问意图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够和Striker战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Striker X3752目前的行为不属于同盟的军务范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以认定为交战对象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我能和中校战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对该问题的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已超出本机作为驾驶员支援启发系统的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何情况下 战斗方针的制定均交由贵官判断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 使用无线会被拦截
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接传达给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么重大的使命 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能飞往加尔刚蒂亚的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 拯救大家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可欠我一个人情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 进入临战态势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,partb
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔…刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔刚蒂亚…要被袭击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人开着冲浪风筝飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能听梅露蒂的 改变航路进行避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的立场 不得不这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德让我们逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算自己去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算代替我们 一个人去战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了保护加尔刚蒂亚 甚至不惜和过去的同伴反目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们却要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他作出了选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须作出选择才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 该是使用那把钥匙的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身负舰团贤者之任的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依据职责建议舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是使用之时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 希望你也能助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为让世界领略我伟大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领略伟大的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.19,0:14:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布 新的圣战就此打响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将会得到胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为给这个星球带来绝对的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为将这个星球建设成安宁华贵的理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从于我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是通往恒久幸福的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 这玩笑可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是同盟战士该有的发言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是银河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是人类居住的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的未来是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球上有着活在这里的人们所建立的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有理由破坏它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等的正义不变」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「别犹豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 这是神之间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力怎么会这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测其威力并非来源于内部发生器 而来源于外部装备的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保存自身能量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 给这颗星球带来新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你快撤 这是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你们也不怎么讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个装神弄鬼的玩意更让人不爽一万倍！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一发 准备好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不参战的普通居民在装甲区域内躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船是本舰团的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能成为攻击目标 请做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饶恕叛乱 反抗的全都是敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我就是这么粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你还挺男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我踹开他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以在战略上确保有利地位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议采取打即跑战术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.48,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(724,650)}Hit-and-run Tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击敌机头部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀死中校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机的机动性凌驾于本机之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「无论强者还是弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「均依靠自身的理性相互扶持」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这才能称为人类吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生器 以最大功率输出！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我说 雷德」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「愿不愿意与我一起改变这个星球？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始接近敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入紧急开仓信号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还好有你在」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 还愿意 跟随我…吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿势控制系统 重启
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 贵官的抵抗是毫无意义的

